icnicking with family and friends Capture beautiful pictures of the lake Have fun doing boating, kayaking, canoeing and river rafting Have a taste of beverages and snacks at local shops and stalls 10. Khajjiar Also referred to as "Mini Switzerland of India ", Khajjiar is a small town positioned at a distance of 20 km from Dalhousie. This place has a plentiful natural beauty that draws the attention of travelers from everywhere. Visit a small lake in the midst of grassland and click photos for memories. Visitors can get involved in fun activities like paragliding and create thousands of memories that will last evermore. The nine-hole golf course is the most popular part of Khajjiar, placed in the centre of luxurious greenery. For a great experience, travel here during winter to play in snow. The place is open from Monday to Sunday Entry charges - None Activities to enjoy at the place: Savor local food Handicraft shopping Horse riding, paragliding, zorbing 11. Chamba Chamba is a Himalayan town in Himachal popular for its alluring prehistoric shrines, caves and monuments. It is a haven for a history enthusiast. Placed at an elevation of 996 meters, it sits on the Ravi River's banks. Few people know that Chamba is an unconventional place that provides natural beauty and tranquil environs. Also, not known by many, it is the campground for several camps in the great Himalayan ranges. The place is open from Monday to Sunday Entry charges - None Activities to enjoy at the place: Trekking Witness eye-catching views of Pir Panjal ranges, Zanskar, and Dhauladhar Shop for traditional handiwork and artwork Attend the famous festivals of Minjar Mela (2nd Sunday of August), Suhi Mata Mela (March/April) 12. Dainkund Peak With the scenic views of snow-topped peaks and pleasing valleys, Dainkund Peak is amongst the most popular tourist attractions to explore in Dalhousie. Located at an elevation of 2755 meters above sea level, it is the highest point of this attractive hill town. Trekking to this peak is quite easy whether one is with family or in a couple. Visitors can follow the pathway laid with tall deodar trees and colorful flowers and get to the peak to enjoy a panoramic view of valleys and hills. The place is open from Monday to Sunday Entry charges - None Activities to enjoy at the place: Camping Trekking Visit Pholani Devi Temple and Air Force Station Witness striking views of snow-clad mountaintops. Next TopicTourist Places in Dandeli ? prev next ? For Videos Join Our Youtube Channel: Join Now Feedback Send your Feedback to [email protected] Help Others, Please Share Learn Latest Tutorials Splunk SPSS Swagger Transact-SQL Tumblr ReactJS Regex Reinforcement Learning R Programming RxJS React Native Python Design Patterns Python Pillow Python Turtle Keras Preparation Aptitude Reasoning Verbal Ability Interview Questions Company Questions Trending Technologies Artificial Intelligence AWS Selenium Cloud Computing Hadoop ReactJS Data Science Angular 7 Blockchain Git Machine Learning DevOps B.Tech / MCA DBMS Data Structures DAA Operating System Computer Network Compiler Design Computer Organization Discrete Mathematics Ethical Hacking Computer Graphics Software Engineering Web Technology Cyber Security Automata C Programming C++ Java .Net Python Programs Control System Data Mining Data Warehouse Javatpoint Services JavaTpoint offers too many high quality services. Mail us on [email protected]point.com, to get more information about given services. Website Designing Website Development Java Development PHP Development WordPress Graphic Designing Logo Digital Marketing On Page and Off Page SEO PPC Content Development Corporate Training Classroom and Online Training Data Entry Training For College Campus JavaTpoint offers college campus training on Core Java, Advance Java, .Net, Android, Hadoop, PHP, Web Technology and Python. Please mail your requirement at [email protected] Duration: 1 week to 2 week Like/Subscribe us for latest updates or ne